Preconditions:
The `board` parameter must not be null.
The `word` parameter must not be null.
The `board` parameter must be a 2-dimensional character array.
The `word` parameter must be a non-empty string.

Postconditions:
The method returns `true` if the `word` exists in the `board`.
The method returns `false` if the `word` does not exist in the `board`.
The method modifies the `board` in any way.
The method does not modify the `word` parameter.